title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Fish
description:
The Fish is a compact pin that features an extended wheelbase and time-honored teardrop shape. Expect a medium flex that allows this board to excel as a cruiser or a mellow carver.
Artists: E. Waetzig & H. Patrick
Artist: Nanami Cowdroy
Artist: Derek Nobbs

L: 39.00” W: 8.75” WB: 27.75”
To learn more about the Fish visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/fish/
